<BLOCK1><TI TOCID="II">AFFIDAVIT OF EGOR IVANDAEV</TI>
<P>I, Egor Ivandaev, of the City of Richmond Hill in the Province of Ontario, <BOLD>MAKE OATH AND SAY:</BOLD></P>
<P>1. I am a Senior Fund Manager employed by the Plaintiff and as such have knowledge of the matters hereinafter deposed to.</P>
<P>2. On May 1, 2017 the defendants granted the plaintiff a mortgage (&ldquo;main mortgage&rdquo;) over a property municipally known as [location omitted] (Lewison Property&rdquo;). This was a mortgage for a period of six (6 months) commencing May 1, 2017 securing the principal sum of $725,000.00 and interest thereon at the rate of 13.99% per annum calculated monthly. The mortgage provides for payment by monthly instalments of $8,452.30 to be paid on the first day of each month including June 1, 2017 and the balance, if any, of the said principle sum and interest shall become due payable on November 1, 2017. <BOLD>Attached and marked as Exhibit &ldquo;A&rdquo; is a true copy of the mortgage/charge dated May 1, 2017</BOLD>.</P>
<P>3. The mortgage was secured against another property owned by the Defendant, Yao Jun Sit wherein all payments made under one mortgage would be considered to be payment under the collateral mortgage and default under one mortgage would be considered a default on the other mortgage. The mortgage provided that upon default the mortgagee could at their sole discretion exercise their rights against any or all properties in order to recover all sums due on the mortgage. The collateral property is municipally known as [location omitted] (&ldquo;Lathan Property&rdquo;). <BOLD>Attached and marked as Exhibit &ldquo;A&rdquo; is a true copy of the mortgage / charge dated May 1, 2017</BOLD>.</P>
<P>4. Each mortgage provides that upon default of payment of monies hereby secured or payable, the balance of the principal and interest shall immediately become due and payable at the option of the mortgagee. Each mortgage provides that upon default that the mortgagee shall have quiet possession of the said lands free from all encumbrances. <BOLD>Attached and marked as Exhibit &ldquo;A&rdquo; is a true copy of the mortgage / charge dated May 1, 2017</BOLD>.</P>
<P>5. The mortgage was renewed from time to time and the most recent renewal particulars are as follows:
