<P>7. On November 29, 2018 a Notice of Sale Under Mortgage was commenced and all interested parties were notified that unless the sums were paid on or before January 9, 2019 that the Plaintiffs advised that they would sell the property. Since that time, nothing has been paid towards the property. The defendants continue to reside in the property and it has not been listed, to be sold yet. <BOLD>Ivandaev Affidavit paragraph 11</BOLD>.</P>
<P>8. The statement of defence does not provide any viable defence to the issue of the non-payment of the mortgage. The defendants are in default and the mortgage has become due and payable in full. <BOLD>Ivandaev Affidavit paragraph 12</BOLD>.</P>
